{
  "stem": "23645.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, now-- so you see, what I'm telling you-- all this love and the security that I felt at home and the surrounding around me, and, and what-- the things that my father used to tell about the situation in Poland, I felt secure.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went on going to school, I went on playing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if something happens, my family's going to look after me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "September-- I think it was the 7th or 8th of September-- but it was a beautiful, wonderful day, the sun was shining.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was Sunday, because I didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think I was going to cheder in the morning, and that was in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was playing outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was sort of an Indian-summer day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, you could almost sense the cool breeze, before the sun came out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we saw planes come overhead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Bombs fell and hit one of the-- on the station-- there was a main station in Skarzysko.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when it hit one of the cars, it had some chemicals in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it just-- a bunch of black smoke just pillared out into the air.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people started running all over the place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember my, my mother looking for me, and she found me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she grabbed me, and we ran quickly into a bomb shelter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she gave me a towel of-- soaked in water, that I held to my nose.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because everybody was screaming, gas, gas, looking at the black smoke.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was just chemicals, and of course, there wasn't any gas.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But this, this-- this is the day that I remember sort of shattered the peacefulness and the everyday life.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
